Bagaimana

1056
00:57:04,349 --> 00:57:06,950
Anda membuatku hidup kembali?

1057
00:57:09,290 --> 00:57:10,290
Apa?

1058
00:57:11,720 --> 00:57:12,829
Lingkaran waktunya

1059
00:57:13,460 --> 00:57:15,159
sudah jelas berhenti.

1060
00:57:16,230 --> 00:57:18,460
Bagaimana Anda melakukan ini?

1061
00:57:19,970 --> 00:57:22,329
Nona Lee, kamu sudah ingat?

1062
00:57:22,839 --> 00:57:25,470
Ya, aku

1063
00:57:26,970 --> 00:57:28,169
